---
description: Karate schema validation — assert a response matches a fuzzy schema (types, not exact values)
requires_target: true
requires_auth: false
vars:
  - feature_name
  - resource_path
  - schema
---
Feature: ${feature_name}

  Background:
    * url baseUrl

  Scenario: ${resource_path} matches the expected schema
    Given path '${resource_path}'
    When method get
    Then status 200
    # fuzzy matchers (#string/#number/#uuid/#present) — robust to volatile values
    And match response == ${schema}
